description:
Our Savior tells His disciples to Go, and make disciples of all nations, baptizing them in the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Matthew 28:19. This Heavenly Trio is called the Godhead. Satan and his vast army of fallen fiends are warring against the Godhead and Gods Church; and as part of their infernal tactics, they are creating confusion, distraction, and division among the Lords people about our Heavenly Father, His Son Jesus Christ, and the Spirit of God.

Satans War Against the Godhead will clear up that confusion, protect you from falsehood, deepen your relationship with Jesus, and inspire you to do your part to fulfill His sacred commission so we can go home to a better land.
